            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BF3"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    For neutron flux monitoring"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  For activation obtained in Au and Th samples;",
                " detection efficiency dependence from gamma-energy in",
                "0.24-0.66 MeV range was defined by 9 gamma-lines of",
                "standard gamma-sources Ba-133, Eu-152, Cs-137.",
                "Efficiency for Au - 3.398E-2 +-3.4%,",
                "           for Th - 2.148E-2+-3.5% .",
                "    Additional test measurement was made in FEI to",
                "check efficiency for Au using thermal neutron",
                "irradiation, other Ge(Li) detector by 4PI-Beta-gamma",
                "coincidence method."
